# ðŸŽ¨ Flask MadLibs Story Generator

An interactive MadLibs web app built with **Python (Flask)**, **HTML/CSS**, and **Bootstrap**.  
Users can choose a story template, fill in words, and generate a custom story in the browser.  

## Features
- 3 story templates (Cold November Day, Zoo Day, Crazy Family)
- User input via HTML forms
- Dynamic story generation using Flask + Jinja2
- Custom CSS styling (rainbow header) with Bootstrap integration

## Tech Stack
- Python, Flask
- HTML, CSS, Bootstrap
- Ready for deployment on Render

## Run Locally
```bash
git clone https://github.com/YourName/flask-madlibs.git
cd flask-madlibs
py -m pip install flask gunicorn
py -m flask run

